Package: mycoBinR
Title: Functions to organize and analyze metagenome data
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Paul", "Muehlauer", email = "paul.muehlauer@student.tugraz.at", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for managing and analyzing fungal genome assembly data, 
    including file path organization, coverage analysis, and taxonomic classification. 
    Facilitates streamlined workflows for bioinformatics projects involving fungal genomes.
